@startuml
title UC06 Credential owner disables a credential or revokes a grant

actor "Credential owner" as Owner
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore

Owner -> UI: Open the credential or grant management screen
UI -> Firestore: Load the owner's credential and grant lists
Firestore --> UI: Lists
UI --> Owner: Show the credential and grant lists

Owner -> UI: Select the target and submit
UI -> API: Request disable or revoke
API -> Firestore: Disable the credential\nor mark the grant as revoked
Firestore --> API: Update complete
API --> UI: Disable or revoke succeeded
UI --> Owner: Show completion
@enduml
